Description:
IN A WORD SPECTACULAR CENTRAL LOCATION
A BEACHHOUSE construction and tweaked by a master builder to create this large, light filled, bright open spacious home… When you step inside you are greeted with warm modern and functional home with a great sense of space, light and a full northerly aspect overlooking your very private outdoor area.
The large formal under cover entry invites you into the 1st living zone with a central kitchen, large benches and stainless steel appliances with northerly windows and sliding doors leading out to a private indoor/outdoor room which creates a huge additional all year round living space. The polished hardwood timber floors have the glass look giving you that open feeling throughout, A wood heater and split systems offer you year around comfort. The master bedroom offers its own en-suite and walk in robe. The 2nd living zone is a great place for the kids and a further 2 bedrooms gives you plenty of room for your guests, The main bathroom and laundry facilities are also located in this area. All this is with a short stroll to the centre of town. This exclusive home offers a child and pet friendly yard with a double garage and ample room for your boat or caravan.
An absolute must if you are looking for the perfect holiday or permanent home.

Description:
When Quality Counts
This Brand New 4 Bedroom family home is built in the excellent Shoalhaven Estate within 1.6km approx to pristine Cowes north facing beach. With a 6 star energy rating, and many other upgrades including open plan living with bamboo flooring, modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, designer tapware, porcelain floor & wall tiles, full ensuite to master, split system air-conditioner, LED down lights to living, 2700mm high ceilings, and oversized double garage with remote. Two large bi-fold doors lead out to the covered alfresco area and separate BBQ area with gas point. Basic landscaping is completed along with fully concreted drive, alfresco area and path wrapping around the home. All this and more is sitting on a 614sqm (approx) parcel of land. If you are looking for a newly built home without the wait time, then this is a must to inspect today!

The beautiful home with an excellent floor plan, comprises three good sized bedrooms including the master with ensuite and walk in robe, a family bathroom including a bath and separate shower, two living areas as well as great outdoor spaces. The main open plan kitchen, living and dining area has sliding doors to the alfresco areas for easy living, indoors and out. A stylish and practical kitchen boasts a 900mm wide stainless steel upright cooker, dishwasher, and a fantastic butlers pantry complete with sink, stone bench tops and a fantastic servery window to the outdoor area; perfect for entertaining.
The double remote garage has internal access whilst there is also access to the huge rear yard for boat or caravan storage.
The well positioned property would make a wonderful permanent home or holiday retreat within walking distance to the shops, cafes, supermarkets, school, medical centre, etc and the amazing north facing Cowes beach.
Other great features of this fantastic home include: timber plank flooring, split system heating and cooling, concrete driveway

Position Perfect!

Description:
TITLED SEAGROVE BLOCK WITH WATER VIEWS
The ultimate site to construct your dream coastal home, with potential water views form a second level. This titled, (668 m2 approx), vacant allotment faces directly toward Cowes north beaches, and presents as a rare opportunity to acquire a coastal block ready for building your contemporary seaside haven. Surrounded by quality homes, this corner block is located in a quiet court, close to the mature eucalyptus trees which form part of a remnant Grassy Woodland considered to be of regional conservation significance. The Sweet Bursaria release features an underground gas (LPG) network and ultra-fast optic fibre connections to the National Broadband Network. Just 800m from the main street of Cowes and even closer to the beach, be quick to secure this rare opportunity to acquire a titled block ready to built on.

Description:
STYLISH TOWNHOUSE
Modern townhouse tucked securely in a gated community resort only 100m from the beautiful Cowes foreshore Beach.
The home has been beautifully designed with space for the entire family. The upper level features two bedrooms with inbuilt wardrobes, family bathroom, modern kitchen, stylish open plan dining and lounge area with large light filled windows and access to an upper level balcony. The lower level offers two bedrooms, family bathroom and European laundry. The home has an attached spacious double car garage with inbuilt secure cupboards. The rear courtyard offers a private retreat with space to relax in the sun with a coffee and good book.
Additional features include full security system and split system heating and cooling on both levels.
The home is located in a small secure community with dual gated access and resort style facilities including in-ground heated pool and community bbq and eating area, and is located a short stroll from the Cowes foreshore beach and yacht club.
Immaculately presented and ready to enjoy, secure this beautiful property in time for Summer. Arrange your private inspection today.
